- support for zmq 3.1

  + context
    + new init/destroy
    + options

  - message:
    + options
    + 'more' function
    + send/recv functions

  - socket
    + send/recv and sendmsg/recvmsg functions, as already in Tcl api
    - send/recv iov ???
    + options
      + HWM -> SNDHWM/RCVHWM
      + SWAP remove
      + MCAST_LOOP remove
      + RECOVERY_IVL_MSEC remove
      + MAXMSGSIZE
      + MULTICAST_HOPS
      + RCVTIMEO
      + SNDTIMEO
      + IPV4ONLY
      + LAST_ENDPOINT
      + FAIL_UNROUTABLE

    + also set/get iso setsockopt/getsockopt
    + flags for send/sendmore/recv (also in 2.1)
